<body>
Reports a string concatenation. Suggests replacing it with a  <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Template_literals">template literal</a>
<p>Example</p>
<pre><code> "result: " + a + "." </code></pre>
 <p>After applying the quick-fix the code looks as follows:</p>
 <pre><code> `result: ${a}.` </code></pre>

</body>
</html>